port - 8080

port change can be done in server.xml -> vi server.xml, type '/connector', insert (i) , change port to 8090 , Esc :wq! 
systemctl restart tomcat -> port change will come into effect now

Apache tomcat runs on Catalina (servlet container)

    Servlet - a Java programming language class that is used to extend the capabilities of servers that host applications accessed by means of a request-response programming model
    Servlet container - a program that manages and executes servlets

/var/logs/tomcat ->  tomcat logs
tomcat_home/conf/server.xml - tomcat config file 


diff btw vi & vim -> vim (colourful)

